                Monimus <lb n="2"/>Ierombali <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>mil</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> c<expan><ex>o</ex><abbr>hor</abbr><ex>tis</ex></expan> I <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>Ituraeor</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan> L <expan><abbr>stip</abbr><ex>endiorum</ex></expan> XXI <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>ic</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> est
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Reliefstele. Der untere Teil fehlt heute. Unklar, ob Ende Z. 5: XVI (neuere Publ.) oder XXI (CIL). Autopsie R. Wiegels.</p>
            </div>
